cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.DB 

This paper discusses the attack surface of Blockchain technology, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and distributed computing (cs.DC). It also covers smart contract attacks, which fall under software engineering (cs.SE), and privacy attacks, which are related to cryptography (cs.CY) and database security (cs.DB).
